Interface Communication

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Invitation, Message, OnlineStatus, UserList
    public interface Communication
    Interface to allow generic communication objects that can be processed into children objects Message and UserList. Will eventually include child object Registration in future iterations.

      • getCommType

        int getCommType()
        Getter method stub for the type of communication.
        Returns:
        The type of communication, currently possibilities are Communication.MESSAGE and Communication.USERLIST. Communication.REGISTRATION will be implemented in future iterations of the WragrIM project.
